---
title: Shrimp Saganaki with Spicy Marinara, Feta, and Israeli Couscous
description: Greek food has so much more to offer than just gyros and tzatziki. Introducing bold and flavorful shrimp saganaki! In this dish, tender shrimp are layered with spicy tomato sauce, olives, and tangy Feta cheese.
